data.description: Gorgeous Home in Menifee, upgrades throughout, 55+ single story home, situated on a tranquil master planned community of Sun City. Great curb appeal, double door entry, Pergo Portfolio waterproof laminate flooring extends throughout the dining room, kitchen & hallway,  Upgraded kitchen with brown cabinetry, newer appliance, recessed dimmer lights, granite counters (ADA) counter section, open to nook/dining area, 5 cieling fans, Master bedroom, with vanity area, French doors, large mirrored closetdoors, large walk in closet, master bath with upgraded counters, mirror, jucuzzi tub/shower, hall bath located off the 2nd bedroom, covered Patio Oasis enclosed with double draped Lattice/Mesh walls, security door exits onto an additional open air patio fenced and gated. Home offers a awesome storage structure Approx. 9 1/2' X 16' WITH 15' High ceiling, built in shelving 7 plenty of room for your golf cart. Rear yard is completly fenced with double door gate for RV Parking, lemon & Lime fruit trees, garden area. Community amenities include, 2 pools, spa, fitness center, tournament shuffleboard court, lawn bowling, horseshoe pits, variety of clubs & activities. Very Low HOA and Taxes.
